// QAM
show int qam 3/1.1 downstream
  - show RF parameters

show int qam 3/1.1 cable
  - same as show int qam 3/1.1

show int  qam 3/1.1 cable psi
  - show PAT and PMTs

show int  qam 3/1.1 cable pat
  - show PAT

show int  qam 3/1.1 cable pmt
  - show PMT

show int  qam 3/1.1 cable carousel
  - show carousels


// Video routes
show cable video route
show cable video route qam 3/1.1
show cable video route qam 3/1.1 route-type
  - show video policy routes



// Video session 
show cable video session [all]
  - summary of video sessions

show cable video session [session-id <id>] [statistics] [in | out]
show cable video session [session-id <id>] [statistics] in [PSI | PAT | PMT]
show cable video session [session-id <id>] [statistics] out [PSI | PAT | PMT]


// Protocol
show cable video ssp gqi
show cable video ssp sdv


// Server group
show cable video sg <name>




// Remaining command found in control plane FS
show int qam-domain <n> route-map [detail]
show cable <slot> video session [summary]
show cable <slot> video session {active | idle | local | remote}

